#: control/forms/admin/admin.py:17 control/forms/global_settings.py:451
msgid "Perform update checks"
msgstr "Sök efter uppdateringar"

#: control/forms/admin/admin.py:19
msgid ""
"During the update check, eventyay will report an anonymous, unique "
"installation ID, the current version of eventyay and your installed plugins "
"and the number of active and inactive events in your installation to servers "
"operated by the eventyay developers. We will only store anonymous data, "
"never any IP addresses and we will not know who you are or where to find "
"your instance. You can disable this behavior here at any time."
msgstr ""
"Under uppdateringskontrollen kommer eventyay att rapportera ett anonymt, "
"unikt installations-ID, den aktuella versionen av eventyay, dina "
"installerade insticksprogram samt antalet aktiva och inaktiva evenemang i "
"installationen till servrar som drivs av eventyay-utvecklarna. Endast anonym "
"data lagras, aldrig IP-adresser, och det går inte att identifiera vem som är "
"eller var instansen finns. Detta beteende kan när som helst inaktiveras här."

#: control/forms/admin/admin.py:28
msgid "Email notifications"
msgstr "E-postaviseringar"

#: control/forms/admin/admin.py:30
msgid ""
"We will notify you at this address if we detect that a new update is "
"available. This address will not be transmitted to eventyay.com, the emails "
"will be sent by your server locally."
msgstr ""
"Avisering skickas till den här adressen om en ny uppdatering upptäcks. "
"Adressen överförs inte till eventyay.com; e-postmeddelandena skickas lokalt "
"av servern."

